These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
City: london, boston
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, black
1. the person who likes green is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| City         | boston   | london |
| Color   | green  | black      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different pets are kept: frog, hamster
House: palace, cape-cod
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
2. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the software-developer is not to the right of the librarian##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the cape-cod house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Pet    | frog        | hamster    |
| House       | palace         | cape-cod |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
